Some scripts I use.

cscope_gen.sh: Help to generate cscope cross-reference
ediff:         Invoke emacs ediff
gitdiff.sh:    Used in gitconfig as external diff program
wallpaper:     Download wallpapers
valgrind.sh:   Help to invoke valgrind
vt:            Help to access several specific kvm hosts and virtuals

Config
------
Add clone repository directory to PATH.
